## ðŸ“š **Extra: Glossary of Big Words**

| Word | Simple Explanation |
|------|-------------------|
| **Embedding** | A list of numbers that represents meaning |
| **API** | A messenger between your app and other services |
| **Database** | A super-organized filing cabinet |
| **Prompt** | Instructions you give to AI |
| **RAG** | Using documents to help AI answer questions |
| **Semantics** | The meaning of words (not just spelling) |
| **Chunk** | A piece of a larger document |
| **Confidence Score** | How sure the AI is about something (0-100%) |
| **Hallucination** | When AI makes up information |
| **Latency** | How long something takes to happen |

